Package client.model

Class Client

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
client.model.Client
public class Client extends javafx.application.Application
Client class is responsible for the connection to the server and for storing the properties connected with the GUI. It also holds the main method which starts the Application.
Author:
Can Ren, Chiara Welz, Rajna Fani, Yuliia Shaparenko
